 pulled 30 feet towards the center of the vortex. Being displaced by the vortex reduces your speed to 0 until the end of the targets next turn. If a target is pulled into the center from this, they take another 55 (10d10) bludgeoning damage. On a success, the target takes half damage and is not moved. When a target starts its turn in the vortex they must repeat the saving throw."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Detect","desc":"The Warden makes a Perception check."},{"name":"Ray of Frost","desc":"The Warden makes one beam attack with Ray of Frost."},{"name":"Obliterate (either) (Costs 2 Actions)","desc":"The Warden either uses Prepare Obliterate to get an obliterate attack ready or Slam Obliterate to bring the obliterate attack down."},{"name":"Vortex (Costs 3 Actions)","desc":"The Warden uses its Vortex attack."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"con","order":2},{"name":"int","order":3}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str","note":" (ex)"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis","note":" (ex)"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"cold","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"fire","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"force","note":" (Vulnerable)","type":"v"},{"name":"lightning","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"},{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"psychic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"conditions":[{"name":"blinded"},{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"deafened"},{"name":"exhaustion"},{"name":"frightened"},{"name":"grappled"},{"name":"incapacitated"},{"name":"paralyzed"},{"name":"petrified"},{"name":"poisoned"},{"name":"prone"},{"name":"restrained"},{"name":"stunned"}],"languages":[{"name":"Deep Speech","speaks":false}],"understandsBut":"cannot speak it","shortName":"","pluralName"